2. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes a monocular vision pipeline for route repetition, which involves computer vision techniques such as SLAM and ground planarity estimation. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper may involve machine learning techniques for training and optimizing the visual pipeline. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper may involve AI techniques for decision-making and control of the autonomous vehicle. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper may involve control theory and system design for achieving high-accuracy path following.
